org.opendaylight.yang.gen.v1.urn.opendaylight.flow.table.statistics.rev131215

Interface OpendaylightFlowTableStatisticsListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.NotificationListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    InventoryAndReadAdapter, StatNotifyCommitTable

    public interface OpendaylightFlowTableStatisticsListener
extends org.opendaylight.yangtools.yang.binding.NotificationListener
    Interface for receiving the following YANG notifications defined in module opendaylight-flow-table-statistics
    (Source path: META-INF/yang/opendaylight-flow-table-statistics.yang): 
     notification flow-table-statistics-update {
     description
         "Receive flow table statistics update";
     leaf id {
         type node-id;
     }
     list node-connector {
         key "id"
         leaf id {
             type node-connector-id;
         }
         uses node-connector;
         anyxml node-connector-context {
             status CURRENT;
         }
     }
     list flow-table-and-statistics-map {
         key "table-id"
         leaf table-id {
             type table-id;
         }
         leaf active-flows {
             type counter32;
         }
         leaf packets-looked-up {
             type counter64;
         }
         leaf packets-matched {
             type counter64;
         }
         uses generic-table-statistics;
     }
     leaf transaction-id {
         type transaction-id;
     }
     leaf moreReplies {
         type boolean;
     }
     uses multipart-transaction-aware;
     uses node;
     uses flow-table-and-statistics-map;
     status CURRENT;
 }
